1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,170
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,170 --> 00:00:03,710
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,710 --> 00:00:05,280
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:06,910 --> 00:00:08,250
(Episode 100)

5
00:00:48,290 --> 00:00:49,990
Why do you want to come with me?

6
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:53,220
We can't just end things like this,
Tae Seok.

7
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,100
You're trying to mess
with my head again.

8
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:02,630
Hye Ra, you despise me.

9
00:01:02,970 --> 00:01:04,440
I despise you.

10
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:05,970
No...

11
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,110
I despise myself even more.

12
00:01:15,250 --> 00:01:17,250
If I hadn't chosen you,

13
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:22,090
none of this tragedy
would have ever happened.

14
00:01:24,290 --> 00:01:25,490
I'm the one who started this.

15
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:29,560
My choices, my ambitions...

16
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:33,330
I accepted your obsession
and possessiveness.

17
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:36,940
This is the price I have to pay.

18
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:40,510
Hye Ra...

19
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:47,750
I have to be the one to end this.

20
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:05,330
- What are you doing?
- Let's end it here!

21
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,130
- Don't!
- Let go!

22
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,830
- Hye Ra, I said let go!
- Die with me!

23
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:16,710
(Under Construction)

24
00:02:52,810 --> 00:02:54,950
(Keep Out)

25
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,310
Jung Won.

26
00:03:58,540 --> 00:03:59,540
Ha Neul.

27
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,380
Why are you being so reckless?

28
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:06,380
Are you trying to drive me crazy?

29
00:04:06,990 --> 00:04:08,090
How did you find me?

30
00:04:08,150 --> 00:04:10,690
Who else would know where you are?
You fool.

31
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:12,320
Jin Tae Seok.

32
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:15,160
- He'll be here.
- No, he won't.

33
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:17,000
No, he can't.

34
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,230
Because Advisor Han Hye Ra
went to find him.

35
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:23,870
Where's my mom now?

36
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:26,740
She's probably with Jin Tae Seok.

37
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,040
I have a bad feeling about this.

38
00:04:42,890 --> 00:04:44,060
Are you asleep, Grandma?

39
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:48,690
Are you listening to your bells?
Come on, open your eyes already.

40
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:50,960
- What was your question again?
- What?

41
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:53,770
I asked what's going to happen
to Jin Tae Seok.

42
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:56,170
Is he really done for
just like that?

43
00:04:59,170 --> 00:05:02,670
The stench of blood is overwhelming.
How terrifying.

44
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,080
- Blood...
- Blood?

45
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,910
Is Jin Tae Seok bleeding?

46
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,820
- Han Hye Ra!
- Wake up, ma'am!

47
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,770
I never thought
I'd live to see the day...

48
00:05:28,370 --> 00:05:30,670
when I, the toughest woman alive,

49
00:05:30,670 --> 00:05:34,910
would end up caring for Han Hye Ra,
the scariest one of all.

50
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:42,380
You were at my throat, and now you
suddenly miss my tender loving care?

51
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:43,510
What are you even doing here?

52
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:51,360
You scared me.
Don't open your eyes so suddenly.

53
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:56,730
What happened? Tell me.

54
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:02,630
(Under Construction)

55
00:06:14,650 --> 00:06:16,780
Did you make sure?

56
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:20,020
I saw him bleeding out...

57
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,190
with my own two eyes.

58
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:26,520
I'm asking if you saw him
take his last breath.

59
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:29,030
No, not exactly, but...

60
00:06:29,790 --> 00:06:31,430
Yeong Soo.

61
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:34,170
- You asked for me?
- I need you...

62
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:36,430
to go check on Jin Tae Seok.

63
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:38,440
Where did you say
the accident happened?

64
00:06:51,450 --> 00:06:52,820
Father.

65
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:55,420
You're supposed to die by my hands.

66
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,320
I won't let anyone else kill you.

67
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:08,570
What?
You couldn't find Jin Tae Seok?

68
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:11,170
That's right. The car was totaled.

69
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,800
It's unlikely he survived.

70
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,410
But you couldn't find a body.

71
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,780
Who do you think took him?

72
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,290
Chairman Joo Ha Neul?

73
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,490
- What about my mom?
- She's resting.

74
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:34,630
Is she okay?

75
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:38,130
Of course. She was in the care
of the toughest woman in the world.

76
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:39,960
Thank you.

77
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:50,540
What is this warm, fuzzy feeling?
Am I becoming a good person?

78
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:53,240
If this keeps up,
I'll become Gong the Good-hearted.

79
00:07:57,110 --> 00:07:58,350
Were you...

80
00:07:59,050 --> 00:08:00,520
trying to die with Jin Tae Seok?

81
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:03,290
I couldn't let him get to you.

82
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:08,260
Because I knew he'd try to kill you.

83
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:12,730
Don't sacrifice yourself
for me anymore, Mom.

84
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:14,900
Look who's talking.

85
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:19,200
Stop sacrificing yourself
for me, Jung Won.

86
00:08:21,770 --> 00:08:25,580
I was so scared
something had happened to you.

87
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:29,280
Me too.

88
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:33,050
What about Jin Tae Seok?

89
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:59,240
You snuck Jin Tae Seok out,
didn't you, Se Hoon?

90
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,110
What are you talking about?

91
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:03,980
I saw you.

92
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:46,720
- So you caught me.
- Where is Jin Tae Seok right now?

93
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:50,390
- Jin Tae Seok is dead.
- Then where's the body?

94
00:09:50,730 --> 00:09:52,330
There has to be a body, right?

95
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:59,500
- Tell me the truth, Se Hoon.
- And what if I do?

96
00:09:59,570 --> 00:10:00,910
Only then...

97
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,540
can we say that he's truly dead.

98
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:05,340
Do you want him dead...

99
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,650
as much as I do, Mother?

100
00:10:09,810 --> 00:10:11,320
Jin Tae Seok...

101
00:10:12,020 --> 00:10:14,050
ruined you, Se Hoon.

102
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:15,120
But...

103
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:17,460
you're my son.

104
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:21,160
You were my son then,
and you still are now.

105
00:10:24,430 --> 00:10:27,430
I'll be the one to finish
Jin Tae Seok.

106
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:31,000
Let me be the one
to get my hands dirty.

107
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:21,690
You're about to learn
what it's like to live...

108
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,020
without truly being alive,
Jin Tae Seok.

109
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,740
Jin Tae Seok.

110
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:43,510
So this was your fate.

111
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:45,610
Even in death,

112
00:11:46,410 --> 00:11:49,180
you'll never get to meet
Ki Beom in the afterlife.

113
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:52,220
In the fiery pits,

114
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:56,690
scream and suffer for all eternity.

115
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:05,600
Jin Tae Seok,

116
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:08,830
you will now be forgotten...

117
00:12:11,540 --> 00:12:12,770
as a dead man.

118
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,750
What do you mean by that?

119
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:30,290
If Young Chae asks for help,
just help her.

120
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:32,020
Help her with what?

121
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:35,360
This isn't your first time helping
Young Chae behind my back, is it?

122
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:36,960
Here.

123
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:42,530
But what if
Ms. Young Chae's request...

124
00:12:43,370 --> 00:12:45,700
requires me to betray you,
Chairman Gong?

125
00:12:46,270 --> 00:12:48,840
You have too many questions.

126
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,540
Shut your mouth.

127
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:53,280
Why would she say that?

128
00:12:54,110 --> 00:12:56,050
Because she has served Grandma
for too long.

129
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:57,480
Just do as you're told.

130
00:12:57,720 --> 00:13:00,620
What do you want me to do, Grandma?

131
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,950
A late-night guest is on the way.
Get ready.

132
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,960
"A late-night guest?"

133
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:07,260
Manager Gu.

134
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,960
There's just one more thing
I need your help with.

135
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:12,930
I can't. Absolutely not.

136
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,570
You don't even know what I'll ask.

137
00:13:14,570 --> 00:13:15,870
I can't whatever it is.

138
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:18,770
I can't hurt Chairman Gong
any further.

139
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:27,380
What is this?

140
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:29,950
The trump card that will relieve
the pain in your heart.

141
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,620
We can link Madam Gong
and Ha Neul together...

142
00:13:34,850 --> 00:13:36,450
and bring them down.

143
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,730
Joo Ha Neul.

144
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,360
At first,
to keep Chairman Gong in check,

145
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:48,730
he must have bought
The Crown Capital stock.

146
00:13:49,130 --> 00:13:52,170
Next, to push out Jin Tae Seok,

147
00:13:52,570 --> 00:13:54,210
he probably used
David Kay as a front.

148
00:13:54,470 --> 00:13:56,570
So he was just buying up stock
to become chairman?

149
00:13:57,170 --> 00:13:58,180
No.

150
00:13:58,810 --> 00:14:01,080
He deceived the shareholders
by posing as a foreign investor.

151
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:02,910
Behind the scenes,

152
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:05,350
he was playing dirty
with money from loan sharks.

153
00:14:07,050 --> 00:14:08,850
He was planning a hostile takeover
of a major company.

154
00:14:09,020 --> 00:14:12,190
Everyone will be floored to find out
that David Kay is Manager Gu.

155
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:13,290
And you think that's it?

156
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:16,190
What if Chairman Gong Nan Sook,
Kunhyang's majority shareholder,

157
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:20,100
had her secretary secretly buy up
the company's stock?

158
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:23,700
We can send her to prison
for trading under a borrowed name.

159
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:26,670
- Is that even possible?
- We just have to spin it that way.

160
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:29,740
Joo Ha Neul leaked
insider information,

161
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:32,040
and Chairman Gong fronted the money
from a private loan.

162
00:14:33,610 --> 00:14:35,510
And Manager Gu posed
as a ghost investor...

163
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:37,680
to take over Kunhyang.

164
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,790
You gave the stock data
to Young Chae?

165
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:49,630
Chairman Gong told me to give it
to Ms. Young Chae if she asked.

166
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:51,560
Why would you do that?

167
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:54,630
I wanted to see
what Young Chae would do with it.

168
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:57,800
To see if I really raised her wrong,

169
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,770
or if she even thinks
of me as her mother.

170
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,640
I'm sure Young Chae gave it
to Se Hoon.

171
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:06,210
Though I wish she hadn't.

172
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:11,050
Please, stop meddling in my affairs.

173
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:15,050
I hope you'll also give up on trying
to take over Kunhyang.

174
00:15:15,990 --> 00:15:18,420
I don't care about taking over
Kunhyang anymore.

175
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:21,030
It's a shame
about the money I returned,

176
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:22,330
but I have plenty more.

177
00:15:22,330 --> 00:15:24,160
My safes are overflowing with it.

178
00:15:24,930 --> 00:15:26,860
I'll handle the things
you're dealing with my way.

179
00:15:26,930 --> 00:15:28,900
How about going abroad for a while?

180
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:31,470
It'll help clean up this mess.

181
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:34,270
You expect me to leave the mess
I made for you to clean up?

182
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:37,310
As the chairman of Kunhyang,
I'm going to face this head-on.

183
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,480
It's a business decision.

184
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:54,730
Sorry to drop in unannounced.

185
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:58,100
Gong Nan Sook,
you've really lost your fire.

186
00:15:58,400 --> 00:15:59,660
It doesn't suit you.

187
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:03,700
Why would I act tough in front
of the scariest woman in the world?

188
00:16:04,100 --> 00:16:06,700
Especially when I'm the one here
asking for a favor.

189
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:08,670
You're worried about Joo Ha Neul,
right?

190
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:11,610
Because he'll try
to take the fall...

191
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:14,080
for your mistakes too.

192
00:16:15,050 --> 00:16:17,480
My Ha Neul can't get hurt.

193
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:22,020
Should I get on my knees again?
Or should I just kowtow?

194
00:16:22,090 --> 00:16:25,860
Cut it out. This isn't fun at all.

195
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:26,960
Han Hye Ra.

196
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,490
Come on, darling.

197
00:16:29,930 --> 00:16:32,960
- You'll help me, right?
- With what? How?

198
00:16:35,930 --> 00:16:36,930
What?

199
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:39,100
You're saying you're going
to take the fall?

200
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:48,210
If the Chairman goes down,
all of Kunhyang goes down with him.

201
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:50,180
You can't make this decision lightly.

202
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:53,880
(Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

203
00:16:53,950 --> 00:16:55,490
This was not an easy decision.

204
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:57,320
I've given it a great deal
of thought.

205
00:16:57,350 --> 00:16:59,890
You don't have to be
the one to step up.

206
00:17:00,190 --> 00:17:01,930
Chairman Gong
will handle it herself.

207
00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:03,160
As the chairman
of the Kunhyang Group,

208
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:04,430
it's my duty to take responsibility.

209
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:06,830
Madam Gong isn't who she used to be.

210
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:08,570
If she goes to prison this time,
she'll be in for a long time.

211
00:17:08,670 --> 00:17:09,870
Ha Neul.

212
00:17:09,930 --> 00:17:14,810
Advisor Han, I need you
to fill my seat while it's vacant.

213
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:29,790
(A few days later)

214
00:17:37,060 --> 00:17:38,700
I'm Lieutenant Min Sung Ho...

215
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:39,960
of the Seoul Police
Financial Crimes Unit.

216
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:42,900
Joo Ha Neul, you're under arrest
for violating the Real-Name Act...

217
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:45,270
and illegal trading
under the Capital Markets Act.

218
00:17:45,270 --> 00:17:47,940
You have the right to an attorney
and a chance to make a statement.

219
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:49,370
Ha Neul.

220
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:52,810
I was expecting this.

221
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:56,080
Don't worry about me.
Please take care of the company.

222
00:18:18,870 --> 00:18:21,140
- What's going on?
- Chairman Joo Ha Neul...

223
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:22,940
has been placed
under emergency arrest.

224
00:18:24,810 --> 00:18:28,410
What? Ha Neul is at the station?
This is too soon.

225
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:30,710
He's trying to take
all the blame himself.

226
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:34,790
But still, he should've given me
time to do something for him.

227
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:36,190
I guess he didn't want...

228
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:38,690
you to get dragged into this.

229
00:18:55,210 --> 00:18:56,210
How are you holding up?

230
00:18:56,610 --> 00:18:59,110
Well, you've been
in a holding cell yourself.

231
00:18:59,410 --> 00:19:01,610
You think a young, healthy guy
like me can't handle it?

232
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:07,620
- Hey! I hired a lawyer for you.
- I don't need one.

233
00:19:08,290 --> 00:19:09,920
Kunhyang has its own legal counsel.

234
00:19:11,690 --> 00:19:14,360
I suppose
that might be better, actually.

235
00:19:16,190 --> 00:19:17,490
Did you book your flight?

236
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:21,030
Of course.
I'm Gong Nan Sook for a reason.

237
00:19:21,170 --> 00:19:23,400
I'm as quick as a cat.

238
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,800
Until things quiet down,

239
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:26,640
don't come back.

240
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:29,070
I said, don't worry.

241
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:31,540
So don't skip your meals here,

242
00:19:32,210 --> 00:19:34,750
and make sure you chew properly.
Got it?

243
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:38,380
I like the prison meals.
Don't worry about me.

244
00:19:40,980 --> 00:19:42,120
I'm worried about you, Mother.

245
00:19:42,990 --> 00:19:45,020
Don't you go skipping meals
just because I'm not around.

246
00:19:58,800 --> 00:19:59,840
What?

247
00:20:00,870 --> 00:20:03,570
Wait, what happened to
Chairman Joo Ha Neul?

248
00:20:03,810 --> 00:20:06,410
He was arrested?
But he's such a stand-up guy.

249
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:10,280
- He was arrested for a reason.
- Young Chae, he's your brother!

250
00:20:10,610 --> 00:20:13,280
- How can you talk like that?
- Must I defend him as family?

251
00:20:13,780 --> 00:20:15,920
If he did something wrong,
he should face the consequences.

252
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:22,560
You get home this instant!

253
00:20:31,340 --> 00:20:32,700
Looks like she schemed again.

254
00:20:35,940 --> 00:20:37,140
Long time no see.

255
00:20:38,210 --> 00:20:39,540
- Director Jin.
- Director Jin.

256
00:20:44,410 --> 00:20:46,350
Are you all better now?

257
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:47,990
I have a lot to catch up on.

258
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:49,250
Let's get to work.

259
00:20:56,360 --> 00:21:00,060
Young Chae, did you give Se Hoon
that list of my crimes?

260
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:03,670
- I did.
- Why did you drag Ha Neul into it?

261
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:05,440
Because it's the one thing...

262
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:07,600
that would hurt you the most.

263
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:09,510
Young Chae.

264
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:10,970
This is what you get...

265
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:13,640
for loving him more than me,
even though he's not your biological son.

266
00:21:15,050 --> 00:21:16,250
So be sad.

267
00:21:17,050 --> 00:21:18,120
Suffer.

268
00:21:19,220 --> 00:21:21,790
- As you watch Ha Neul get broken...
- Joo Young Chae!

269
00:21:22,390 --> 00:21:24,760
How could you turn out so twisted?

270
00:21:25,190 --> 00:21:28,030
Of all people,
you went after your own brother?

271
00:21:28,190 --> 00:21:30,790
If you don't want to be arrested,
you should flee the country.

272
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:33,100
After all,
that's what Gong Nan Sook would do.

273
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:48,510
You look so pale.

274
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:52,320
I never thought I'd call you here.

275
00:21:53,580 --> 00:21:54,850
Did Ha Neul say anything?

276
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:57,190
You know, some brilliant plan
to stay out of jail.

277
00:21:57,520 --> 00:22:00,920
You know that brilliant plan,
Madam Gong.

278
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:02,560
Do I?

279
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:06,130
I know that Young Chae and Se Hoon
framed Ha Neul.

280
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:10,730
Young Chae, that little brat,
how could she backstab her brother?

281
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:15,210
Se Hoon is even more vindictive
than Young Chae.

282
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:17,510
And Se Hoon is another story.

283
00:22:18,740 --> 00:22:20,280
He's not even
Jin Tae Seok's biological son.

284
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,680
How can he be so vicious?

285
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:24,580
But you also did something...

286
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:27,180
unforgivable to Se Hoon, didn't you?

287
00:22:28,990 --> 00:22:30,890
I really drove a dagger...

288
00:22:31,320 --> 00:22:33,520
through Se Hoon's heart, didn't I?

289
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,330
I can't deny that, ma'am.

290
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:38,960
Even though you were just a pawn
in Jin Tae Seok's game,

291
00:22:40,260 --> 00:22:42,630
what you did to former Vice Chairman
Jin Se Hoon's mother...

292
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:46,700
Yes, you're right about that.

293
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:50,540
I can admit when I'm wrong.

294
00:22:50,770 --> 00:22:54,110
Then I assume you know
what you have to do.

295
00:22:59,620 --> 00:23:02,490
(Civil Complaint Information Desk)

296
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,960
Excuse me.

297
00:23:17,230 --> 00:23:18,370
Excuse me.

298
00:23:18,970 --> 00:23:20,000
How can I help you, ma'am?

299
00:23:20,570 --> 00:23:24,040
I'm here to turn myself in.

300
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:26,140
And what crime did you commit?

301
00:23:27,180 --> 00:23:30,310
I'm not sure of the official charge.

302
00:23:30,780 --> 00:23:32,120
Solicitation of murder?

303
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:33,750
What?

304
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:37,620
There's also illegal stock trading
using a borrowed name,

305
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:39,760
and something
that's basically embezzlement.

306
00:23:44,130 --> 00:23:46,060
All right, slap the cuffs on me.
Quickly.

307
00:23:48,170 --> 00:23:49,170
Go on.

308
00:23:50,430 --> 00:23:52,040
Chairman Gong...

309
00:23:54,970 --> 00:23:57,570
Don't cry on an empty stomach.
Eat up, then cry all you want.

310
00:24:01,380 --> 00:24:03,010
She's the sweetest girl
in the world,

311
00:24:03,410 --> 00:24:05,420
but I called her a wicked witch
and cursed her out.

312
00:24:05,950 --> 00:24:07,320
For a son that isn't even her own,

313
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:09,820
and she cherishes
more than her own child,

314
00:24:10,490 --> 00:24:13,860
she sacrificed herself,
for crying out loud.

315
00:24:38,150 --> 00:24:41,050
I can't forgive you
for the things you've done.

316
00:24:43,390 --> 00:24:44,390
But...

317
00:24:46,190 --> 00:24:49,360
can I believe
that your love for me was real?

318
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:57,300
I'm going to believe it was.

319
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:02,570
Why can't I bring myself
to just hate you?

320
00:25:09,080 --> 00:25:10,080
Dad.

321
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:13,480
Just try to live normally in there.

322
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:18,380
Gong Nan Sook turned herself in.

323
00:26:22,020 --> 00:26:24,960
I guess she had a conscience,
after all.

324
00:26:27,220 --> 00:26:28,260
Hye Ra.

325
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:31,260
You can rest now.

326
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:36,100
Fall asleep here beside me.

327
00:26:38,370 --> 00:26:39,370
Forever.

328
00:26:49,110 --> 00:26:50,280
Your voice...

329
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:54,950
used to be so comforting and sweet.

330
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,360
There was a time...

331
00:27:02,730 --> 00:27:05,160
when just hearing your voice
made my heart skip a beat.

332
00:27:07,700 --> 00:27:08,930
I love you.

333
00:27:11,530 --> 00:27:12,540
I know.

334
00:27:15,740 --> 00:27:18,270
I know how much you loved me.

335
00:27:23,210 --> 00:27:24,250
But now,

336
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:27,920
it's time your love ended.

337
00:27:30,990 --> 00:27:32,590
I never knew...

338
00:27:35,330 --> 00:27:38,260
my love was suffocating you.

339
00:27:42,230 --> 00:27:43,600
Was my love...

340
00:27:47,470 --> 00:27:48,670
a sin?

341
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:55,210
Was it so grave...

342
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:59,450
that I deserve to die for it?

343
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:20,670
(A Graceful Liar)

344
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:44,430
Are you saying
you committed the murder yourself?

345
00:28:44,490 --> 00:28:47,600
Are you hard of hearing, detective?
I said he's dead.

346
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:48,930
He's like an immortal, isn't he?

347
00:28:48,930 --> 00:28:50,600
I'm worried
he might rise from his own grave.

348
00:28:50,700 --> 00:28:53,770
This misery started when I became
the matriarch of Kunhyang,

349
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:56,870
and from my ambition
to reach the very top.

350
00:28:57,010 --> 00:28:59,140
Do we get karma too?

351
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:00,540
Not guilty? How's that possible?

352
00:29:00,610 --> 00:29:02,850
Chairman Gong Nan Sook
turned herself in.

353
00:29:03,150 --> 00:29:05,350
Se Hoon will be the chairman
of Kunhyang Group again soon.

354
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:07,050
It was never my place to begin with.

355
00:29:07,050 --> 00:29:10,290
I must atone for my own sins.

356
00:29:10,690 --> 00:29:12,890
I won't be able
to visit you for a while.

357
00:29:16,890 --> 00:29:18,930
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
